casebody.data:
Brenda HOOGENSTYN, Plaintiff-Appellant,
v.
ORTHOPAEDIC ASSOCIATES OF GRAND RAPIDS, PC, and Julian Kuz, M.D., Defendants-Appellees,
and
Walker Surgical Center, LLC, and Michael Burton, Defendants. SC: 156220
COA: 332063 Supreme Court of Michigan. May 29, 2018

Order

On order of the Court, the motion for reconsideration of this Court's February 20, 2018 order is considered, and it is DENIED, because it does not appear that the order was entered erroneously.
